	ocation Link:\n\nBroadview Branch\n\nRoom Location: Meeting Room\n\nDetail
	ed Description: This service is free and available to individuals only. Th
	e free service is not available for business tax returns. To receive tax h
	elp\, bring the following documents:\,\n\nRequired:\n\nPhoto identificatio
	n\, Social Security cards or Individual Taxpayer Identification Numbers \\
	(ITIN\\) for everyone listed on the tax return.\, Proof of income\, for ex
	ample\, W2s and 1099s \\(Social Security benefits\\)\, Official documents 
	on Social Security Administration letterhead\, Medicare card \\(if Social 
	Security number is followed by an "A"\\)\, Be prepared to provide informat
	ion about health care coverage for each person on the return.\,\n\nRecomme
	nded:\n\nLast year&'s tax return\, if available\, Bank account and routing
	 numbers for direct deposit of refunds\, Photocopies or computer print-out
	s of any of these documents willbe accepted.\, Due to federal budget cuts 
	the IRS is unable to provide the Library with certain tax forms and instru
	ction booklets.\, Most IRS forms are available online at\n\nwww.irs.gov .\
	, You may make free black-and-white prints of the forms from Library compu
	ters:\n\nwww.spl.org/Print \, Thanks to our partner\n\nAARP .\n\nEvent Log
	istics: AARP Tax Help locations serve anyone who earned less than $80\,000
	 in 2025.\, For eligibility details\, contact AARP at 888-227-7669.\n\nCon
	tact Us: If you have questions about this event\,\n\nAsk Us\n\nor call 206
	-386-4636.\n\nADA Accommodations: We can provide accommodations for people
	 with disabilities at Library events. Please\n\ncontactLEAP\n\nat least se
	ven days before the event to request accommodations.\, All Library program
	s are free and open to the public.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/
	#/details/free-tax-help/18162991/2026-03-30T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Arts & C
	ulture
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/free-tax-help/18162991/20
	26-03-30T00
